those features is being developed for version 0.3.5:
+ add Java client library
+ add advanced features for Xen: live migration, hot backup
+ management for VM not started by nova
+ user ACL made optional
+ better VM image management for NFS mode (add "power off" option)
+ host machine power management
+ better install script

those features are proposed for version 0.4:
+ re-implemented master in C, better concurrency
+ lightweight and faster worker, asset node
+ client libraries (Java, Python, Ruby) and command line tools (Python)

